Remediation Steps:
      *) Isolate the infected host by removing "DESKTOP-L8C5GSJ"
  from the Network to prevent Lateral Movement
     *) Reset Passwords: Force a password reset for the User "shutchenson0"
     *) Block: Update Firewalls to block/hold traffic to the "authenticatoor.org" & "google.authenticatoor.burlesson-appliance.net" domains.
     

